tags.lyrics:
[Intro]
Yeah

[Verse 1]
I&#039,ve been tryna call
I&#039,ve been on my own for long enough
Maybe you can show me how to love, maybe
I&#039,m going through withdrawals
You don&#039,t even have to do too much
You can turn me on with just a touch, baby

[Pre-Chorus]
I look around and
Sin City&#039,s cold and empty (Oh)
No one&#039,s around to judge me (Oh)
I can&#039,t see clearly when you&#039,re gone

[Chorus]
I said, ooh, I&#039,m blinded by the lights
No, I can&#039,t sleep until I feel your touch
I said, ooh, I&#039,m drowning in the night
Oh, when I&#039,m like this, you&#039,re the one I trust
Hey, hey, hey

[Verse 2]
I&#039,m running out of time
&#039,Cause I can see the sun light up the sky
So I hit the road in overdrive, baby, oh

[Pre-Chorus]
The city&#039,s cold and empty (Oh)
No one&#039,s around to judge me (Oh)
I can&#039,t see clearly when you&#039,re gone

[Chorus]
I said, ooh, I&#039,m blinded by the lights
No, I can&#039,t sleep until I feel your touch
I said, ooh, I&#039,m drowning in the night
Oh, when I&#039,m like this, you&#039,re the one I trust

[Bridge]
I&#039,m just walking by to let you know (By to let you know)
I can never say it on the phone (Say it on the phone)
Will never let you go this time (Ooh)

[Chorus]
I said, ooh, I&#039,m blinded by the lights
No, I can&#039,t sleep until I feel your touch
Hey, hey, hey
Hey, hey, hey

[Outro]
I said, ooh, I&#039,m blinded by the lights
No, I can&#039,t sleep until I feel your touch
